{"tid":273393,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[直覺塔羅] 你問我答（6月號）","createTime":"2017-06-06T13:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T07:36:37.000Z","uid":14621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b18df4827323b1e96d9ceccc5946a7aad2f98bb","tid":273393,"uid":14621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:40:19.000Z","msg":"六揀一&nbsp;<br />\n範疇：愛情 / 友情 / 家庭 / 事業 / 學業 / 健康&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n將你揀既範疇send去我 FB/IG，叫聲我「巴打」就會有一個指定嘅Plan Free俾你。<br />\nIG：<a href=\"http://instagram.com/spirinatural/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fspirinatural%2F&d=cTx%2FBqCQlkm1oPdLuvFJhWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=f2cba983\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/spirinatural/</a><br />\nFB：<a href=\"http://facebook.com/spirinatural/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fspirinatural%2F&d=cTx%2FBqCQlkm1oPdLuvFJhWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a99f87c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/spirinatural/</a><br />\n<br />\n塔羅Q&amp;A：<br />\n1.要俾啲咩資料<br />\n無論幫人問定自己問，姓名、高度、三圍，通通都唔駛俾我，淨係講件事就喇。<br />\n<br />\n2.塔羅牌禁忌<br />\n全無禁忌，唔駛戒口，唔怕未散功就講粗口。<br />\n<br />\n3.有冇妖魔鬼怪係裡面<br />\n我既塔羅無任何妖魔鬼怪，亦全任何宗教成份，塔羅牌就只係紙牌一張，我只係將上天想向你講既說話翻譯俾你聽。<br />\n假如你有信仰架話，你可以向你既宗教神單聲，話有條友會用塔羅牌幫你問野。<br />\n<br />\n4.之前搵過其他占卜，會唔會有對衝<br />\n首先如果其他占卜師有俾建議你嘅，就應該跟住做咗先。假若件事已經過咗一排，而你又覺得件事比先前有啲唔同，就已經可以再搵占卜師。<br />\n<br />\n5.要點樣問<br />\n你唔駛識點問，你只需要將心中疑問連同相關故事同我講就可以。<br />\n<br />\n6.點樣抽牌<br />\n網上做唔需要你親自抽牌，我會幫你搞晒，你淨係等我份Report就得喇。<br />\n<br />\n7.試咗準至再追加<br />\n我一見到依d說話，就會將你放到最後至覆，等同於有條友問你，試咗同你扑野係爽既先至溝你，你自己都覺被侮辱啦。<br />\n<br />\n8.幾耐至收到回覆<br />\n因為我工作不定時，所以未必即時回覆大家，仲要視乎多唔多人問，因為我係順時序覆Message，總之一定唔會miss。<br />\n<br />\n9.想做課金plan可以點俾錢<br />\n我有恆生/中銀/PayPal[+10%]。"},{"pid":"4c1f395ed7ac6bbdf0771089d262a8238a130c9f","tid":273393,"uid":14621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb1a3a5dd33b4604a0ed32852888bb47e83f1d0","tid":273393,"uid":71574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b1d5fc8c0150970a003f15b97dc1343559bb69","tid":273393,"uid":14621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:36:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}